edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.router
Class StaticSourceHandler

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.router.StaticSourceHandler

public class StaticSourceHandler
extends java.lang.Object

This class separates the static nets in to separate nets so they can be routed more easily by the router. This same process happens in Xilinx PAR during the routing phase.

Author:
Chris Lavin Created on: Jun 10, 2010
